title: Red Ryder BB Guns & Cual es tu Fantasia
itunes:title: Red Ryder BB Guns & Cual es tu Fantasia
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling, and Marc Sessler – discuss the latest news from around the NFL, including Broncos quarterback Brock Osweiler getting the start over an injured Peyton Manning, and a full break down of the beef between Texans defensive end JJ Watt and Bengals quarterback Andy Dalton. Plus, the long-awaited return of “Cual es tu Fantasia?”
